程序包 com.example.cmput301project.model

类 Event

java.lang.Object
java.util.Observable
com.example.cmput301project.model.Event
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable
public class Event extends Observable implements Serializable
Represents an Event in the system. An Event has a waitlist of entrants, a limit for participants, and information such as name, description, poster URL, and QR codes.
作者:
Xinjia Fan
